Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.45,0:04:23.53,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(186.8,131.201)}Váyanse a la concha de su madre
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.57,0:04:24.41,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(180.4,280.23)}Qué basura
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.86,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(346.8,147.901)}No me lo creo
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.62,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(221.429,63.43)}¿Quién es esta chiruza?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.94,0:04:19.98,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(259.143,21.715)}Todas las idols\Nson unas falsas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.99,0:04:24.20,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(218,3.43)}Traidora. No vuelvo a ir\Na un concierto de ella.
