Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.45,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(2,25.716)}Se acabó todo,\Ntodo todito.
