Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.74,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(458,110.288)}Voy a quemar\Ntodos mis productos de ellas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.87,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(371.143,61.716)}Si esto es cierto,\Nque le diga chau a su carrera
