Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.87,Cart_A_Tre,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\bord1\fs12\c&H9793A7&\3c&HF9F7FC&\pos(58,256.002)}Coge como todo el mundo
